title: In J&K, Modi announces projects worth Rs 20,000 cr, private investment of Rs 38,000 cr - ThePrint
content: In J&K, Modi announces projects worth Rs 20,000 cr, private investment of Rs 38,000 cr  ThePrintView Full coverage on Google News
description: In 1st visit to J&K since abrogation of Article 370, PM also inaugurated solar power plant at Palli village in Samba district, making it India's 1st 'carbon-neutral' panchayat.
